<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>OPENHOUSE MATEMÁTICAS</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --gold: #d6a42f;
      --gold-soft: #f1d27a;
      --brown: #6b3f18;
      --brown-dark: #2e1d10;
      --cream: #f8ecd0;
      --wine: #7a3b18;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #2a180d 0%, #4a2a14 35%, #1f140d 100%);
      color: var(--cream);
    }

    header {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 95vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(214,164,47,0.35), transparent 35%),
        linear-gradient(rgba(33, 20, 12, 0.58), rgba(33, 20, 12, 0.82)),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503676260728-1c00da094a0b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    header::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(214,164,47,0.10), rgba(107,63,24,0.08));
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      max-width: 950px;
      background: rgba(46, 29, 16, 0.55);
      border: 1px solid rgba(241, 210, 122, 0.22);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      padding: 28px 24px 34px;
      border-radius: 28px;
    }

    .logo-wrap {
      width: 132px;
      height: 132px;
      margin: 0 auto 18px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(248,236,208,0.95), rgba(241,210,122,0.82));
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      border: 3px solid rgba(214,164,47,0.85);
    }

    .logo-wrap img {
      width: 106px;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      border-radius: 18px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4.4rem);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-shadow: 0 3px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.18rem;
      color: var(--cream);
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .cta {
      margin-top: 24px;
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #b78319);
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      color: var(--brown-dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.20);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .cta:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 26px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
    }

    main {
      max-width: 1140px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 46px 20px 60px;
    }

    section {
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      background: rgba(248, 236, 208, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(241, 210, 122, 0.16);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
    }

    h2 {
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 1.65rem;
    }

    p {
      color: #f5ead7;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px,1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(107,63,24,0.72), rgba(46,29,16,0.92));
      padding: 22px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      transition: 0.25s ease;
      border: 1px solid rgba(241,210,122,0.15);
      color: var(--cream);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.20);
      border-color: rgba(241,210,122,0.35);
    }

    .gallery {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px,1fr));
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .gallery img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 2px solid rgba(241,210,122,0.20);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.20);
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 2px solid rgba(241,210,122,0.18);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(0,0,0,0.20);
      background: #000;
    }

    .stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px,1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stat {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(248,236,208,0.08), rgba(107,63,24,0.40));
      padding: 24px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(241,210,122,0.18);
    }

    .stat h3 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin: 0 0 6px;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--gold-soft);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      background: #1a1009;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--gold-soft);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(241,210,122,0.14);
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .hero {
        padding: 24px 18px 30px;
      }

      .logo-wrap {
        width: 112px;
        height: 112px;
      }

      .logo-wrap img {
        width: 90px;
      }

      iframe {
        height: 240px;
      }

      section {
        padding: 22px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="logo-wrap">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Logo de la escuela">
    </div>
    <h1>OPENHOUSE MATEMÁTICAS</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Licenciatura en Enseñanza y Aprendizaje de las Matemáticas</p>
    <a class="cta" href="#video">Ver proyecto</a>
  </div>
</header>

<main>

<section>
  <h2>¿De qué trata?</h2>
  <p>
    OPENHOUSE MATEMÁTICAS es una experiencia académica donde futuros docentes presentan proyectos, materiales y estrategias didácticas innovadoras.
    Este espacio permite compartir el impacto real del aprendizaje matemático con otras instituciones.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Objetivos</h2>
  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">Innovar en la enseñanza de las matemáticas</div>
    <div class="card">Mostrar proyectos reales de estudiantes</div>
    <div class="card">Conectar instituciones educativas</div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Impacto del proyecto</h2>
  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat"><h3>+50</h3><p>Estudiantes</p></div>
    <div class="stat"><h3>+10</h3><p>Proyectos</p></div>
    <div class="stat"><h3>100%</h3><p>Participación</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Evidencias</h2>
  <div class="gallery">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509062522246-3755977927d7">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513258496099-48168024aec0">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f">
  </div>
</section>

<section id="video">
  <h2>Video del proyecto</h2>
  <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ"></iframe>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Contacto</h2>
  <p><strong>Escuela:</strong> Escuela Normal Superior "Profr. Moisés Sáenz Garza"</p>
  <p><a href="http://www.normalmsg.edu.mx/ens" target="_blank">Ir al sitio oficial</a></p>
</section>

</main>

<footer>
  OPENHOUSE MATEMÁTICAS · Escuela Normal Superior "Profr. Moisés Sáenz Garza"
</footer>

</body>
</html>
